description:
A Lego Stop Motion Music video for tobyMac's song, Beyond Me. Enjoy!

Well, it's been about a year, so I guess it is about time for me to post a video. I have gone back to my roots, making another music video for you all to enjoy. If you enjoyed the video, please leave a like, favorite the video, and share it with your friends! If you did not like the video, please leave a comment telling me what I can improve! If you would like to see more videos, please check out my channel and subscribe! As usual, I do not own this song!
